{
  "text": "Federated learning produces personalized recommendation models by communicating model building between a central server and mutually disconnected peers holding personal information [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . Thus, federated learning enacts model building centrally on data that is distributed across personal data owners.",
  "correct_citation": {
